main event: Observer watched a round-shaped object overhead moving towards the west faster than any known aircraft, maintaining a steady course and altitude of approximately 10,000 feet.
interesting points: The object changed speed without any specific data available,The sighting lasted for a total duration of 4 hours and 10 minutes,The object was visible continuously during that time,The witness described the object as having a white color and making a sound like a blaring siren,The object was estimated to be about 5,000 feet away.
witness description: The witness provided detailed responses to a questionnaire regarding the sighting.
